model.hed: 12 Versatile Sneakers to Last You Through the Fall
model.dek: As we start to layer up and replace our summer T-shirts with sweaters, henleys, and crewnecks, it's important to remember your shoes must go through the same process. That canvas pair you bought back in May? They're over the hill and it's time to put them out to pasture. Replace them with something more substantial, something warmer, and maybe even something tweed. Here are 12 pairs that you can wear with nearly anything in your wardrobe. Let the great seasonal swap begin!

items.title: Veja Suede Sneakers
items.caption:
Classic athletic-inspired kicks. You can't go wrong.

*$130, available at [kithnyc.com](http://kithnyc.com/collections/footwear/products/veja-holiday-black-nautico)*

items.title: VANS WOOL SPORT AUTHENTIC
items.caption:
The sneaker you love, in a fabric that matches the season.

*$55, available at [vans.com](http://www.vans.com/shop/wool-sport-authentic-pewter-white)*

items.title: Valentino Rockrunner
items.caption:
As luxe as a sneaker can get (figures it's from Valentino).

*$975, available at [valentino.com](http://www.valentino.com/us/sneaker_cod44898822jt.html)*

items.title: Tiger of Sweden soft suede sneakers
items.caption:
Simple, clean, and [suede](http://www.gq.com/gallery/six-ways-to-wear-suede-fall) (it's a big thing for fall, trust us).

*$230, available at [ssense.com](https://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/tiger-of-sweden/grey-suede-sneakers/1174153)*

items.title: Greats Graphite Suede Sneaker
items.caption:
Go for something neutral and dark with just enough detail to keep it interesting. 

*$169, available at [greats.com](http://www.greats.com/products/the-royale-graphite-suede)*

items.title: LANVIN SNEAKER IN WOOL FELT AND NAPPA CALFSKIN
items.caption:
A sneaker that will become a closet staple. 
$570, *available at [lanvin.com](http://store.lanvin.com/us/sneakers_cod44861910nj.html)*

items.title: Del Toro Dotted Velvet Chukka Sneaker
items.caption:
The velvet sneaker, a total Costanza move that we actually condone.

$340, *available at [deltoro.com](http://www.deltoroshoes.com/men/chukkas/men-s-black-dotted-velvet-chukka-sneaker.html)*

items.title: New Balance x Premier 998
items.caption:
No color combo better than black and tan this fall.

*$220, available at [kithnyc.com](http://kithnyc.com/collections/footwear/products/new-balance-x-premier-m998)*

items.title: Aldo Wool Sneakers
items.caption:
Stay in wool, stay toasty.

*$75, available at [aldoshoes.com](http://www.aldoshoes.com/us/en_US/men/shoes/c/210/MINNITAKI/p/40268060-97#)*

items.title: Diemme  Grey Tweed Sip-On Sneakers $25
items.caption:
This is what happens when your favorite suiting material hits your favorite sneaker. Bliss.

*$250, available at [ssense.com](https://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/diemme/grey-tweed-slip-on-garda-sneakers/1281603)*
